Functions:


1. Positional Arguments
	--- Can be given as direct values based on positions in the definition
	--- Can also be given as keyword arguments
	--- Required Arguments
		** missing 1 required positional argument

2. Keyword Arguments
	--- Can be given from the call of the function
	--- Required arguments
		** missing 1 required positional argument
	--- can be defined at the calling of function

3. Default Arguments
	--- Positional arguments should not follow default arguments
	--- Required Arguments should not follow default arguments
	--- keyword only arguments can be interchangable with default arguments
	--- Can only be defined at the definition of function

4. Positional Only Arguments
	--- Cannot also be given as keyword arguments
	--- all arguments before / are positional only arguments
	--- Can only be defined at the definition of function

5. keyword only arguments
	--- Can only be defined at the definition of function
	--- all arguments after * are keyword only arguments